title: Magellan 2008/2009 Map Data
description:
Magellan Roadmate 1412 2008/2009 Map Data + 6 million POI file
This is a backup from a 1412 Roadmate with Revision 31 2008/2009 Maps.
This should work with many other Roadmate units.  Just backup the old files to your system first and copy these into their place.  On the Maestro 3225 its on the TFAT partition, on the Roadmate it maps a separate Removeable Disk drive letter to store the map files.
